Bahrain,Center,SMS,allows,users,to,send,both,English,and,Arabic,text,messages,English,messages,can,have,up,to,characters,and,Arabic,messages,can,have,up,to,characters,The,Bahrain,Center,SMS,API,allows,users,to,integrate,the,ability,to,send,SMS,messages,and,view,their,SMS,points,into,their,own,application